@EndNode

@Node "WRID" "RxSerial Warning, Requirements, Installation and Distribution"

  @{u}@{b}Warning, Requirements, Installation and Distribution@{ub}@{uu}


    Warning
        THIS SOFTWARE AND INFORMATION ARE PROVIDED AS IS.
        ALL USE IS AT YOUR OWN RISK, AND NO LIABILITY OR
        RESPONSIBILITY IS ASSUMED. NO WARRANTY IS MADE,

    Requirements
        o The library needs:
              . AmigaOS, version 3 or higher

    Installation
        o Run the installer script
        o The library dispatch offset is -30

    Distribution
        @{u}RxSerial is Freeware@{uu}

        You are free to distribute it as long as the original archive
        is kept intact. Commercial use or its inclusion in other
        software package is prohibited without prior written consent
        from the Author.

@EndNode

@Node "Terms" "RxSerial Terms"

  @{u}@{b}Terms@{ub}@{uu}


    The main terms used in this guide are:

        o @{b}ID@{ub}
          The serial object descriptor as returned by @{"SERCreate()" LINK "SERCreate"}

        o @{b}Types of arguments:@{ub}

              . D    Any data    --    --
              . N    Numeric     /N    ARexx integral number
              . S    Symbol      /S    ARexx valid symbol
              . V    StemName    /V    As S but with length<32
              . O    StemName    /O    As V but maybe "" also

@EndNode

